### 1. 예약 등록
# @name createReservation
POST {{base_url}}/api/v1/reservations
X-User-Id: {{user_id}}
X-User-Role: USER
X-Waiting-Token: {{waiting_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "restaurantId": "{{restaurant_id}}",
  "timeSlotId": "{{time_slot_id}}",
  "reservedDate": "2026-06-01",
  "slotStartTime": "18:00:00",
  "guestCount": 2,
  "courses": [
    {
      "courseId": "{{course_id}}",
      "quantity": 1,
      "unitPrice": 50000
    }
  ]
}

> {%
  client.global.set("reservation_id", response.body.data.reservationId);
  client.test("201 Created", () => client.assert.response.status === 201);
%}

###

### 2. 내 예약 목록 조회
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/reservations?status=CONFIRMED&page=0&size=10
X-User-Id: {{user_id}}

> {%
  client.test("200 OK", () => client.assert.response.status === 200);
%}

###

### 3. 예약 상세 조회
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/reservations/{{reservation_id}}
X-User-Id: {{user_id}}
X-User-Role: USER

> {%
  client.test("200 OK", () => client.assert.response.status === 200);
%}

###

### 4. 예약 수정 — guestCount만 변경
PATCH {{base_url}}/api/v1/reservations/{{reservation_id}}
X-User-Id: {{user_id}}
X-User-Role: USER
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "guestCount": 3
}

> {%
  client.test("200 OK", () => client.assert.response.status === 200);
%}

###

### 4-1. 예약 수정 — 날짜 + 슬롯 변경 (slotStartTime 필수)
PATCH {{base_url}}/api/v1/reservations/{{reservation_id}}
X-User-Id: {{user_id}}
X-User-Role: USER
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reservedDate": "2026-06-10",
  "slotStartTime": "19:00:00"
}

> {%
  client.test("200 OK", () => client.assert.response.status === 200);
%}

###

### 5. [Internal] 예약 유효성 확인
GET {{base_url}}/internal/reservations/verify?userId={{user_id}}&restaurantId={{restaurant_id}}

> {%
  client.test("200 OK", () => client.assert.response.status === 200);
%}

###

### 6. [Internal] 체크인
PATCH {{base_url}}/internal/reservations/check-in
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reservationId": "{{reservation_id}}",
  "restaurantId": "{{restaurant_id}}"
}

> {%
  client.test("200 OK", () => client.assert.response.status === 200);
  client.test("status COMPLETED", () => {
    client.assert.response.body.data.status === "COMPLETED";
  });
%}

###

### 7. [Internal] 예약 이력 존재 확인
GET {{base_url}}/internal/reservations/exists?reservationId={{reservation_id}}&userId={{user_id}}&restaurantId={{restaurant_id}}

> {%
  client.test("200 OK", () => client.assert.response.status === 200);
%}

###
